-- Asia Cement CEO Sees 30 Yuan a Ton Cement Price Increase, Standard Reports
-- B y   D e b r a   M a o
-- 2010-09-26T23:44:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-26/asia-cement-ceo-sees-30-yuan-a-ton-cement-price-increase-standard-reports.html
Asia Cement (China) Holdings Corp.
Chief Executive Chang Tsai-hsiung said the average selling price
of cement may rise 20 to 30 yuan a ton this year, the Standard
reported.  Chang said government restrictions on power-use has caused
a shortage in the supply of cement in eastern China, the report
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
